{"tid":2273124,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解香港人咁鍾意中英混合","createTime":"2020-11-05T13:35:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T05:08:10.000Z","uid":300420,"like":3,"dislike":62,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"975e607ffc929fb2c75102561ec34945b8c75d13","tid":2273124,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:35:23.000Z","msg":"講嘢用廣東話<br />\n但係寫嘢要用英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有啲仲衰嘅寫嘢用拉丁化廣東話拼音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鬼睇得明咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我寧願佢同我純英好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要喺廣東話+英文+廣東話同英文嘅拼音混合體（係一種由兩種語言文法及詞彙混合而成 難以理解 隨個人而變化嘅新型土話）中自由切換真係好撚難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最重要係最後嗰個 唔知點解無論係大學定係工作都有人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n班友到底有冇返過學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"379f4d9a6256af2ede8bed68e15d81879ad0ac10","tid":2273124,"uid":34503,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:36:03.000Z","msg":"文化"},{"pid":"e23da1d09a8cf4f2be236eeed91dbc9d139b750c","tid":2273124,"uid":300420,"like":1,"dislike":32,"score":-31,"quote":{"pid":"379f4d9a6256af2ede8bed68e15d81879ad0ac10","tid":2273124,"uid":34503,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:36:03.000Z","msg":"文化"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:37:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢種文化令到香港人好難同非香港人溝通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a3e6e28d7276fa268a7c737cc92a67ca5def462","tid":2273124,"uid":217098,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:38:10.000Z","msg":"本地化姐<br />\n馬來文都係咁"},{"pid":"619f4dca5e527d975a